Crawford Wilson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crawford_Wilson 0 Crawford "Crawdaddy" Wilson (born September 9, 1989) is an American actor and voice actor, from Memphis, Tennessee. He is best known for playing the lead role of Sagi in the Nintendo GameCube role-playing video game Baten Kaitos Origins. He also voiced Jet in the animated series Avatar: The Last Airbender.
